    • Method Detail

      • stepEarly

        void stepEarly​(ec.util.MersenneTwisterFast random)
        Performs actions for early apoptosis phase.

        Cell decreases in size due to cytoplasmic water loss and nuclear pyknosis. Cell will transition to late apoptosis after completing STEPS_EARLY steps at an average rate of RATE_EARLY.

        Specified by:
        stepEarly in class PottsModuleApoptosis
        Parameters:
        random - the random number generator

      • stepLate

        void stepLate​(ec.util.MersenneTwisterFast random,
              Simulation sim)
        Performs actions for late apoptosis phase.

        Cell continues to decrease in size due to cytoplasm blebbing and nuclear fragmentation. Cell will complete apoptosis after completing STEPS_LATE steps at an average rate of RATE_LATE.

        Specified by:
        stepLate in class PottsModuleApoptosis
        Parameters:
        random - the random number generator
        sim - the simulation instance
